\begin_inset Formula $L$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $S$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $J$
\end_inset

。在节
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "sec:1-13"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

, 我们曾得到了两个量子数为
\begin_inset Formula $j_{1}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $j_{2}$
\end_inset

的角动量耦合而生成的总角动量量子数, 为
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
j=j_{1}+j_{2},j_{1}+j_{2}-1,j_{1}+j_{2}-2,\cdots,|j_{1}-j_{2}|\tag{\ref{eq:1-207}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
应用这一结论, 很容易得到多电子原子的
\begin_inset Formula $L$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $S$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $J$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
对于两个电子的体系, 两个电子的角量子数分别为
\begin_inset Formula $l_{1}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $l_{2}$
\end_inset

, 自旋量子数都是
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{1}{2}$
\end_inset

, 即
\begin_inset Formula $s_{1}=\frac{1}{2}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $s_{2}=\frac{1}{2}$
\end_inset

, 利用(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:1-207"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)式可得
\begin_inset Formula $L$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $S$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $J$
\end_inset

的一系列可能值:  
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
L & =l_{1}+l_{2},l_{1}+l_{2}-l,l_{1}+l_{2}-2,\cdots,|l_{1}-l_{2}|\label{eq:2-98}\\
S & =1,0\label{eq:2-99}\\
J & =L+S,L+S-1,L+S-2,\cdots,|L-S|\label{eq:2-100}
\end{align}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
对于含有三个电子的原子, 角量子数分别为
\begin_inset Formula $l_{1}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $l_{2}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $l_{3}$
\end_inset

, 自旋量 子数为
\begin_inset Formula $s_{1}=s_{2}=s_{3}=\frac{1}{2}$
\end_inset

, 则三个电子的总L可由(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:2-98"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)式的每一个值再与
\begin_inset Formula $l_{3}$
\end_inset

耦合而成, 即
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
L & =l_{1}+l_{2}+l_{3},l_{1}+l_{2}+l_{3}-1,l_{1}+l_{2}+l_{3}-2,\cdots||l_{1}-l_{2}|-l_{3}|\label{eq:2-101}\\
S & =\frac{3}{2},\frac{1}{2}\label{eq:2-102}\\
J & =L+S,L+S-1,L+S-2,\cdots,|L-S|\label{eq:2-103}
\end{align}

\end_inset


\end_layout

