\begin_inset Formula $l_{1}=l_{2}=0$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $s_{1}=s_{2}=\frac{1}{2}$
\end_inset

。得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
L=0,S=1,0
\]

\end_inset

氦原子中两个电子的量子数为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
n_{1}=n_{2}=1,l_{1}=l_{2}=0,m_{1}=m_{2}=0
\]

\end_inset

按Pauli原理, 
\begin_inset Formula $m_{s1}≠m_{s2}$
\end_inset

, 即两电子自旋必须相反, 若令
\begin_inset Formula $m_{s1}=\frac{1}{2}$
\end_inset

, 则
\begin_inset Formula $m_{s2}=-\frac{1}{2}$
\end_inset

, 所以两电子的总自旋磁量子数
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
M_{S}=\sum_{i}m_{si}=0
\]

\end_inset

由(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:2-95"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

