\begin_inset Formula $S=0$
\end_inset

, 即
\begin_inset Formula $S=1$
\end_inset

违反Pauli原理, 这
\begin_inset Formula $S=1$
\end_inset

所对应的谱项(即原子状态)不能存在, 应该去掉, 所以光谱项和光谱支项为 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
{\rm He}(1s^{2}):{}^{1}S,^{1}S_{0}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

