\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
:\varPsi_{n}^{(0)}=\sum_{i=1}^{k}c_{i}^{(0)}\varPsi_{ni}^{(0)}\label{eq:2-142}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

所谓正确的零级波函数指的是使方程(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:2-124"
